name: pense na China (想想中國)
description:
this is the fourth song of our first series 'mambembe AI'.

'os_metasambas' makes language experiments w/ brazilian music and musical collages of stuff like glitchy sounds, funk carioca and electronic music.
@iagovrs (voice, guitar)
@danilomap (beatmaker, arranger)

[letra:]
pense na China
por favor, não se esqueça da China
olhe pra China

não se esqueça que ela olha pra você
ela quer te conhecer
quando a hora chegar

pense na China

[lyrics:]
think about China
please, don’t forget about China
look at China

don’t forget that she looks at you
she wants to know you
when the time comes

think about China
